    answer: `AI SMS costs £${pricing.addOn.price}/month as a channel add-on. Loft conversion projects range from £20,000 Velux conversions to £75,000 mansard builds. One captured enquiry through a timely text — while your competitors' phones sat unanswered on the scaffold plank — pays for the add-on many times across its lifetime.`
  },
  {
